{"tid":2215510,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"四眼比人告了暴動你永遠搞分化；泰博議會投了反對你永遠搞分化","createTime":"2020-09-24T04:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T18:07:11.000Z","uid":38189,"like":11,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3cb8676ca614790860fc755deb77813adb2f5c93","tid":2215510,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:57:40.000Z","msg":"想用一本笑死朕氹你開心　好讓妳能多愛投我一票<br />\n落選的滋味　妳不懂這種感覺　早有泛民鐵票的妳永遠不會<br />\n<br />\n看見鄺俊宇在我面前　證明我努力只是愚昧<br />\n市民不懂我的　那些憔悴　是妳永遠不曾過的體會<br />\n<br />\n四眼比人告了暴動你永遠搞分化<br />\n我又何苦勉強自己愛上妳的選票<br />\n妳又狠狠逼退　熱血公民<br />\n靜靜關上門來默數我的淚<br />\n<br />\n泰博議會投了反對你永遠搞分化<br />\n我還傻傻等到五區當選的那一天<br />\n直到那一天　妳會發現<br />\n真正愛妳的熱血公民守著傷悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8a45d8d7aa74db369ee8a8420ee9e8e9c37596","tid":2215510,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:58:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e60de1f153da0e1f9a50ec2e88907fbf7af301c","tid":2215510,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:59:20.000Z","msg":"我還傻傻等到五區當選的那一天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4853039c6f95ffdbe37f04cdaf356b776821d258","tid":2215510,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:59:29.000Z","msg":"改得幾差下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb176eba9ff8f2a3206f9232ffb7ab95dfab394d","tid":2215510,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4853039c6f95ffdbe37f04cdaf356b776821d258","tid":2215510,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:59:29.000Z","msg":"改得幾差下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:00:03.000Z","msg":"我差唔通你叫好咩傻閪冰人"},{"pid":"fe1ba46975c1cd48a8e8488f4f7496f0aa89